org.eclipse.scada.configuration.component

Interface Component

  • All Known Subinterfaces:
    CalculationComponent, ConstantValue, DataComponent, DataMapperAnalyzer, DriverConnectionAnalyzer, ExecJob, ExternalValue, LoadAverage, MappedSourceValue, MasterImportConnectionAnalyzer, PersistentValue, PingCheck, SingleValue, SystemInformationVMStat
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    CalculationComponentImpl, ComponentImpl, ConstantValueImpl, DataComponentImpl, DataMapperAnalyzerImpl, DriverConnectionAnalyzerImpl, ExecJobImpl, ExternalValueImpl, LoadAverageImpl, MappedSourceValueImpl, MasterImportConnectionAnalyzerImpl, PersistentValueImpl, PingCheckImpl, SingleValueImpl, SystemInformationVMStatImpl

    public interface Component
    A representation of the model object 'Component'.

    The following features are supported:

    • Level
    • Customization Pipeline
    • Archive Selector

    See Also:
    ComponentPackage.getComponent()
